Making the history of Defi, Libero Financial Freedom will launch The Worldâ€™s first positive rebase token coming to Centralized Exchanges (CEXes)..
Unlike other rebase tokens which are inflationary and have unlimited supply, LIBERA has a limited supply of 50 millions tokens, of which 18% will be burned at launch, and more will be burned every week based on Libero's 1-4% weekly burning speed. WHAT IS LIBERA

The world's first Triple passive income & Hyper Deflationary token coming to Centralized Exchanges (CEXes)

4,037.20% Fixed APY Auto-Staking

$Libero is auto-compounding inside your LIBERA token at the rate of 1.02% a day or 4,037.20% a year. Unwrap from Libera to Libero at any time

Highest 520% BUSD APR From DEX Trading Volume

Stake in LIBERA Bank to get BUSD passive income from 7% trading volume. The APR is based on current APR of Libero Bank data

Never Seen Before: 8% Passive Income From CEX Trading Volume

$LIBERA is the first ever rebase token that can be listed on Centralized Exchanges (CEX) and get passive income from 8% of their trading volume.

{/* >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>... five feature >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>. */}

HOW IT WORKS

5 features that make LIBERA a game changer in the fixed APY projects

1. A reduction of tax: Buy Fee: 5% Sell Fee: 16%

Unlike other fixed APY projects with a buy fee usually ranging from 13% to 16%. LIBERA buy fee is only 5%. This will encourage users to buy and make bigger volumes and also bring higher buy pressure for LIBERA than other fixed APY projects.

{/* >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> box-7 CHOOSE LIBERA >>>>>>>>>>>. */}

WHY CHOOSE LIBERA

Limited supply with Highest Burning Rate

Unlike other rebase tokens which are inflationary and have unlimited supply, LIBERA has a limited supply of 50 millions tokens, of which 18% will be burned at launch, and more will be burned every week based on Libero's 1-4% weekly burning speed. Even more, for every sell 25% of the tokens are burned - the highest burning percentage in the whole market - make LIBERA a hyper deflationary token never seen before.

Earn high BUSD passive income

You can stake Libera in LIBERA Bank and earn high APR BUSD rewards from both DEXes and CEXes trading volume, plus high LIBERO rewards. For reference Libero Bank rewards are now 642% APR BUSD - highest on the whole Defi market.

Earn 4,037.20% $Libero APY inside itself
